+## Complete Kit — Paid Product ($29 one-time)
+
+The Stack Architect Complete Kit is available at stackarchitect.xyz/pro for $29 one-time via Stripe.
+
+Contents:
+- FILE_01_CAPI_Shield.json — Meta Conversions API v25.0 + Google GA4 Measurement Protocol server-side tracking
+- FILE_02_TikTok_CAPI.json — TikTok Events API v1.3 CompletePayment server-side events
+- FILE_03_Stocky_Swap_Inventory.json — Live inventory to Google Sheets, replaces Shopify Stocky before August 31 2026 shutdown
+- FILE_04_P_and_L_Auto.json — Live profit and loss reporting to Google Sheets (26 data fields per order)
+- SA_Template_1_Stocky_Swap_Inventory.xlsx — Pre-configured inventory sheet with 19 column headers and formulas
+- SA_Template_2_PnL_Auto.xlsx — Pre-configured P&L dashboard with Raw Orders tab, P&L Summary tab, and COGS Table tab
+- README_Complete_Kit.pdf — Full setup documentation and troubleshooting guide
+
+Delivery: Instant access via Stripe redirect to Google Drive folder. No email required. Files permanent.
+Price: $29 one-time. No subscription. No recurring fees. Works on Make.com free tier indefinitely.
+Deployment time: 10 minutes for all four scenarios vs 8+ hours building from free guides.
+The technical outcome is identical to the free guides — EMQ scores, attribution accuracy, and data fidelity are the same.
